data.name: label4.Text
data.value: Hybrid Mode lets you combine both online and offline sources. You can browse and apply themes from the web while keeping your local themes accessible, giving you the flexibility to mix, and preview all your favorites in one place.

data.name: label25.Text
data.value: - It has a layout similar to Windows Explorer for easier use. Create a branch, upload your themes, and finally submit a theme publication request. - Instructions are provided within the manager itself, so you’ll be able to follow them as soon as you open it.
